        {
            "title": "丹麥養老基金AkademikerPension擬賣美債 稱川普政策引發信用風險",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 丹麥養老基金AkademikerPensionkademiker計畫在本月底前賣出美國國債，因擔憂美國總統唐納德·川普的政策已引發不容忽視的信用風險。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該基金首席投資官Anders <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:Schelde;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/Schelde\">Schelde</a>周二向彭博表示：「美國基本上不具備良好的信用狀況，長期來看美國政府財政不可持續。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Schelde透露，為教師和學者管理約250億美元儲蓄的該基金，截至2025年底持有約1億美元美國國債。他強調，風險與流動性管理是其依舊持有美債的唯一理由，「我們已決定，我們可以找到替代選擇」。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-f281da0d-7cd6-3980-b685-80063e609d6d-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Schelde將川普威脅接管格陵蘭列為賣出美債的部分原因。但他同時指出，對財政紀律的擔憂及美元走弱等，同樣構成撤出美國資產的合理依據。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Danish Pension Fund AkademikerPension to Exit US Treasuries</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%B9%E9%BA%A5%E9%A4%8A%E8%80%81%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91akademikerpension%E6%93%AC%E8%B3%A3%E7%BE%8E%E5%82%B5-%E7%A8%B1%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96%E5%BC%95%E7%99%BC%E4%BF%A1%E7%94%A8%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA-134643997.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-20 22:20:21",
