        },
        {
            "title": "馬克龍公開抨擊美國 稱川普貿易策略意在「馴服」歐盟",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"US Census Bureau\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"626\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/OVZHznMa7kc62S90Agrkcw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYyNg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/3c3677c425f1f43aac7d01e94ba438d7\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">US Census Bureau</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 法國總統埃馬紐埃爾·<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:馬克龍;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/馬克龍\">馬克龍</a>抨擊川普的貿易戰略，認為歐洲需要強化主權，以避免「附庸化和鐵血政治」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他公開反對來自美國的競爭，稱美方通過貿易協定破壞歐洲出口利益、要求最大讓步，並公然意圖削弱和馴服歐洲。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">馬克龍在達沃斯世界經濟論壇的演講中表示，這「無休止的新關稅疊加從根本上是不可接受的」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普近日向他的歐洲盟友發出廣泛威脅，稱美國將對不支持其吞併格陵蘭島的國家實施破壞性的貿易措施，川普還因馬克龍拒絕加入加沙和平委員會而威脅對法國葡萄酒徵收懲罰性關稅。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-da4b9245-f89b-3b30-8f3b-b5456a1a776e-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普還在社交媒體上發布了一段來自馬克龍的簡訊，這位法國領導人邀請川普在巴黎共進晚餐，並於周四會見來自烏克蘭、敘利亞、丹麥和俄羅斯的領導人。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這位美國總統周末宣布，將從2月1日開始對八個歐洲國家的商品徵收10%的關稅，除非達成「購買格陵蘭島」的協議，否則關稅將在6月升至25%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">馬克龍警告說，川普的貿易政策正在損害歐洲的出口利益，「要求最大的讓步」。他敦促歐洲人不要接受一種「新殖民主義方式」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這位法國總統還對川普進行了幾次含沙射影的抨擊，其在演講開始時說「這是一個和平、穩定和可預測的時代」，引起了人群的笑聲。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"626\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/I__YjCym.QLwxN9FH_rnfw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYyNg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/bef076a643a7e2e33ab76cd687bc87a9\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">歐洲領導人計畫在周四舉行緊急會議，討論如何應對川普威脅。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Macron Blasts Trump Trade Strategy Meant to ‘Subordinate’ EU (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Nayla Razzouk、James Regan.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%A6%AC%E5%85%8B%E9%BE%8D%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E6%8A%A8%E6%93%8A%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B-%E7%A8%B1%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E7%AD%96%E7%95%A5%E6%84%8F%E5%9C%A8-%E9%A6%B4%E6%9C%8D-%E6%AD%90%E7%9B%9F-162359753.html",
