        {
            "title": "網飛將其與華納兄弟的交易改為全現金方式 以抵禦Paramount的競爭",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 為了與Paramount Skydance Corp.競購好萊塢最具標志性的娛樂公司之一，網飛公司達成了一項修訂後的全現金協議，收購<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:華納兄弟;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/華納兄弟\">華納兄弟</a>探索公司的制片廠和流媒體業務。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據一份申報文件，網飛此前同意以每股27.75美元的現金加股票收購華納兄弟探索的資產，如今將改為全額以現金支付。該文件證實了彭博新聞社此前關於修訂交易條款的報導。華納兄弟探索計畫召開股東特別會議以批准這筆交易。網飛表示，股東應能在4月份之前對該交易進行投票。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-77dd01d8-6204-332c-aa80-ee687f9daa89-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這些變化旨在加快出售進程，並回應Paramount提出的主張：其每股30美元的現金要約收購（針對包括CNN和TNT等有線頻道在內的整個華納兄弟探索公司）更具優勢。作為哥倫比亞廣播公司和MTV的母公司，Paramount一直敦促投資者接納其要約。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">圍繞華納兄弟探索的爭奪戰是多年來規模最大的媒體交易之一，並有可能重塑娛樂行業。Paramount自9月份以來一直強勢追求華納兄弟，而流媒體領頭羊網飛則是意外的求購方，在華納兄弟於10月份宣布尋求出售後網飛才加入競爭。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">網飛聯席執行長Ted Sarandos在一份聲明中表示，華納兄弟董事會「仍然支持並一致建議我們的交易，我們有信心這將為股東、消費者、創作者以及更廣泛的娛樂界帶來最佳結果」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">華納兄弟股價在紐約盤前交易中下跌不到1%，至28.50美元。網飛上漲1.2%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Netflix Amends Warner Bros. Deal to All Cash in Bidding War (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%B6%B2%E9%A3%9B%E5%B0%87%E5%85%B6%E8%88%87%E8%8F%AF%E7%B4%8D%E5%85%84%E5%BC%9F%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E6%94%B9%E7%82%BA%E5%85%A8%E7%8F%BE%E9%87%91%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F-%E4%BB%A5%E6%8A%B5%E7%A6%A6paramount%E7%9A%84%E7%AB%B6%E7%88%AD-131758300.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-20 22:20:23",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "貝森特稱鮑威爾出席最高法院庫克聽證會將是一個「錯誤」",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國財政部長斯科特·<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:貝森特;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/貝森特\">貝森特</a>批評<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:聯儲會;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/聯儲會\">聯儲會</a>主席傑羅姆·<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:鮑威爾;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/鮑威爾\">鮑威爾</a>計畫出席<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:美國最高法院;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/美國最高法院\">美國最高法院</a>周三就總統唐納德·川普試圖罷免聯儲會理事麗莎·庫克一案舉行的聽證會。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">貝森特周二在瑞士達沃斯出席世界經濟論壇期間接受CNBC採訪時表示：「我其實認為這是個錯誤。因為如果你想避免把聯儲會政治化，那麼讓聯儲會主席坐在那裡、試圖把自己的手指按在天平上，是一個嚴重的錯誤。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:貝森特;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/貝森特\">貝森特</a>發表此番言論之際，美國最高法院計畫於周三舉行聽證會，審理川普試圖罷免庫克一事。據一位不願具名的知情人士稱，鮑威爾計畫出席該聽證會。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-6b4332a9-9d70-3a22-a60b-8d6a65a492cc-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：聯儲會主席鮑威爾計畫出席美國最高法院就庫克案舉行的聽證</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">去年12月10日發布會上被問及庫克案時，鮑威爾選擇不予回應。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我們不是法律評論員。案件在法院審理，」他當時表示。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Bessent Says Powell Attending Supreme Court Hearing Is ‘Mistake’</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B2%9D%E6%A3%AE%E7%89%B9%E7%A8%B1%E9%AE%91%E5%A8%81%E7%88%BE%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AD%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E6%B3%95%E9%99%A2%E5%BA%AB%E5%85%8B%E8%81%BD%E8%AD%89%E6%9C%83%E5%B0%87%E6%98%AF-%E5%80%8B-%E9%8C%AF%E8%AA%A4-130623044.html",
